<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٩٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3885">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ أَبِي الْأَسْوَدِ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/634">إِسْمَاعِيلُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1760">خَالِدٍ الْحَذَّاءِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3667">أَبِي قِلَابَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كَانَ الْقُنُوتُ فِي الْمَغْرِبِ وَالْفَجْرِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>